source.name: Storm Data
source.description: Storm Data is a monthly publication of NCDC. Issues from Jan 1959 to the current date are available in the Image Publication System System (IPS). Monthly issues contain a chronological listing by states of storm occurrences and unusual weather phenomena. Reports contain information on storm paths, deaths, injuries, and property damage.
